      <title>中日总理赴首尔举行2019年以来首次会晤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/china-japan-leaders-head-to-seoul-for-first-summit-since-2019</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国、日本和韩国领导人将举行自 2019 年以来的首次三方峰会，东京和首尔之间更紧密的关系给北京带来了压力，要求北京在安全和半导体生产等问题上不能被排除在外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/china-japan-leaders-head-to-seoul-for-first-summit-since-2019</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 01:36:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言在加密货币上诉中援助被定罪的“丝绸之路”创始人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/trump-vows-to-aid-convicted-silk-road-founder-in-crypto-appeal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普呼吁对丝绸之路在线市场创始人罗斯·乌布利希进行减刑，试图将自己定位为自由意志选民支持加密货币的候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/trump-vows-to-aid-convicted-silk-road-founder-in-crypto-appeal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 01:20:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于莫迪的民意调查目标存疑，印度市场准备迎接抛售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/india-s-markets-brace-for-selloff-if-modi-bjp-disappoints-at-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的政党在选举中以微弱优势获胜，印度蓬勃发展的市场将面临抛售风险，这将危及他更广泛的改革计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/india-s-markets-brace-for-selloff-if-modi-bjp-disappoints-at-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克誓言如果保守党获胜，18岁青少年将强制服兵役</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-05-25/mandatory-national-service-for-18-year-olds-if-tories-win-sunak-vows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 宣布，如果保守党在 7 月 4 日的大选中再次获胜，18 岁的年轻人将被迫服某种形式的国民兵役。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-05-25/mandatory-national-service-for-18-year-olds-if-tories-win-sunak-vows</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 23:11:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着债务压力的增加，法国将削减失业救济金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/france-to-trim-benefits-for-jobless-as-debt-pressure-mounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理加布里埃尔·阿塔尔公布了一项削减法国失业救济金的计划，以推进总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的经济改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/france-to-trim-benefits-for-jobless-as-debt-pressure-mounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 22:22:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国极右翼势力在欧盟选举中击败马克龙政党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/french-far-right-seen-trouncing-macron-s-party-in-eu-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据 La Tribune 和 BFM TV 的 Elabe 民意调查，法国极右翼国家联盟在两周后举行的欧洲选举中扩大了对总统马克龙政党的领先优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/french-far-right-seen-trouncing-macron-s-party-in-eu-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 21:28:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克承诺在英国选举策略中实行强制国民服役</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/sunak-pledges-mandatory-national-service-in-uk-election-gambit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保守党表示，将在下届议会结束时恢复实行了数十年之久的每个 18 岁英国人服兵役的规定，这是一场引人注目的政治赌博，因为英国首相里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 在 2019 年大选前阐述了他为期六周的竞选信息。七月选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/sunak-pledges-mandatory-national-service-in-uk-election-gambit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布基纳法索军事领导人将执政至 2029 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/burkina-faso-military-leader-set-to-stay-in-power-until-2029</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布基纳法索将允许军政府领导人易卜拉欣·特拉奥雷参加下届总统选举，成为第二个在军事控制下推迟恢复文官统治的西非国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/burkina-faso-military-leader-set-to-stay-in-power-until-2029</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 18:40:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯对乌克兰家居用品店的袭击造成四人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/war-in-ukraine-russian-bomb-wounds-dozens-at-hypermarket-in-kharkiv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰一名州长表示，周六，一枚俄罗斯滑翔炸弹袭击了哈尔科夫市的一家家居用品超市，造成 4 人死亡、至少 38 人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/war-in-ukraine-russian-bomb-wounds-dozens-at-hypermarket-in-kharkiv</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 15:38:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>多伦多大学要求亲巴勒斯坦抗议者离开校园公园</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/university-of-toronto-tells-protesters-to-leave-threatens-suspensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，多伦多大学在一个庞大的亲巴勒斯坦营地周围张贴了非法侵入告示，警告称，如果抗议者不尽快撤离，将采取“一切必要的法律措施”驱散抗议者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/university-of-toronto-tells-protesters-to-leave-threatens-suspensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 22:14:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
